Raúl Cancio https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ra%C3%BAl_Cancio 0 Raúl Cancio (18 September 1911 – 23 October 1961) was a Spanish film actor, screenwriter and film director. Cancio acted in more than sixty five films including Raza (1942). He also directed two films, a 1952 documentary and a 1950 feature film.
